    "body": "<!-- markdownlint-disable -->\n\n## Purpose\nSUMMARY:\n* separate online quantization into separate QuantizationMethod\n\n## Test Plan\n- run lm eval on the model\n```bash\n# MODEL := \"deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2-Lite\"\n# MODEL := \"RedHatAI/DeepSeek-Coder-V2-Lite-Instruct-FP8\"\n\nlaunch MODEL:\n\tvllm serve {{MODEL}} --quantization fp8\n\neval MODEL:\n\tlm_eval \\\n\t\t--model local-completions \\\n\t\t--tasks gsm8k \\\n\t\t--model_args \"model={{MODEL}},base_url=http://localhost:8000/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False\"\n\n```\n\n## Test Result\n- `just launch deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2-Lite`\n```bash\nlocal-completions (model=deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2-Lite,base_url=http://localhost:8000/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False), gen_kwargs: (None), limit: None, num_fewshot: None, batch_size: 1\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.3624|±  |0.0132|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.3632|±  |0.0132|\n```\n\n- `just launch RedHatAI/DeepSeek-Coder-V2-Lite-Instruct-FP8`\n```bash\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.7733|±  |0.0115|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.7612|±  |0.0117|\n```\n\n- `just launch deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2-Lite` (VLLM_TEST_FORCE_FP8_MARLIN=1)\n```bash\nlocal-completions (model=deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2-Lite,base_url=http://localhost:8000/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False), gen_kwargs: (None), limit: None, num_fewshot: None, batch_size: 1\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.3685|±  |0.0133|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.3692|±  |0.0133|\n```\n\n---\n<details>\n<summary> Essential Elements of an Effective PR Description Checklist </summary>\n\n- [ ] The purpose of the PR, such as \"Fix some issue (link existing issues this PR will resolve)\".\n- [ ] The test plan, such as providing test command.\n- [ ] The test results, such as pasting the results comparison before and after, or e2e results\n- [ ] (Optional) The necessary documentation update, such as updating `supported_models.md` and `examples` for a new model.\n- [ ] (Optional) Release notes update. If your change is user facing, please update the release notes draft in the [Google Doc](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YyVqrgX4gHTtrstbq8oWUImOyPCKSGnJ7xtTpmXzlRs/edit?tab=t.0).\n</details>\n\n",
